text: Kirpichnogo zavoda 1 () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Funtovsky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 3,041 as of 2010. There are 138 streets. == Geography == It is located on the Tsaryov River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Kirpichnogo zavoda 1
